---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ResumeButton from '../components/ResumeButton.astro';
import { profile, tools } from '../data/resume';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] items-start gap-x-4 sm:gap-x-6 md:gap-x-10">
    <img
      src="/profile.jpg"
      alt={profile.name}
      class="col-start-1 row-start-1 h-24 w-24 shrink-0 rounded-full object-cover shadow-md sm:h-32 sm:w-32 md:h-40 md:w-40 md:row-span-3 lg:h-48 lg:w-48"
    />
    <div class="col-start-2 row-start-1 min-w-0">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">{profile.name}</h1>
      <p class="mt-1 text-base text-accent-600 sm:mt-2 sm:text-lg">{profile.title}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-2 mt-6 space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700 md:col-start-2 md:col-span-1 md:mt-4">
      <p>
        Senior software engineer based in Connecticut. I've been building things on the web since around 2008, and noticing when things are a little off for about as long.
      </p>
      <p>
        That's what most of the work on this site is about: the typo, the twenty-five-minute build, the brown sign I can't identify from the highway, the accessibility grade that should be an A instead of a D. The unglamorous stuff that makes the glamorous stuff possible, and the small wins that give teammates their afternoons back.
      </p>
      <p>
        I spent 2021–2025 leading the in-house rebuild of TriNet's corporate website. Vue 2/Nuxt to Vue 3/Astro, D to A on accessibility, and a build pipeline that went from 25 minutes to 1. Before that, DiscoverOrg, a few years of independent consulting, and a winding road through a couple of agencies and front-end gigs going back to the 2000s.
      </p>
      <p>
        When I'm not doing that I'm building my own apps (Brown Sign, Saddle, Kelvin Caliper), or writing, or hiking, or ignoring all of the above.
      </p>
      <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">
        Currently open to senior engineering roles, remote or Hartford-area hybrid.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-2 mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3 md:col-start-2 md:col-span-1">
      <ResumeButton />
      <a
        href="/work"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-slate-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 transition-colors hover:border-accent-600 hover:text-accent-600"
      >
        See My Work
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-20">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Tools & Technologies</h2>
    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      {tools.map((t) => (
        <span class="rounded-full bg-accent-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-slate-700">
          {t}
        </span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
